  "The speed of molecules in a gas": "",
  "The energy needed for a collision": "",
  "The ratio of effective collisions to total collisions due to orientation requirements": "",
  "The total number of collisions per second": "",
  "The steric factor (p) accounts for the fraction of collisions that have the correct orientation. It is typically less than 1 and is multiplied into the collision theory rate equation.": "",
