  "The distribution of products in a reaction": "",
  "The distribution of catalysts in a solution": "",
  "The distribution of molecular sizes in a sample": "",
  "The distribution of molecular kinetic energies (or speeds) at a given temperature": "",
  "The Maxwell-Boltzmann distribution shows the range of kinetic energies (or speeds) that molecules have at a particular temperature, forming a characteristic curve.": "",
