  "The energy released as heat": "",
  "The energy needed to start a reaction": "",
  "The energy of motion, equal to 1/2 mv^2": "",
  "Kinetic energy is the energy a molecule possesses due to its motion, given by KE = 1/2 mv^2, where m is mass and v is velocity.": "",
