  "The importance of temperature": "",
  "The importance of molecular orientation in determining whether a collision is effective": "",
  "The law of conservation of mass": "",
  "This demonstrates the steric factor: even if molecules have enough energy, they must collide in the correct orientation for the reactive atoms to interact and form products.": "",
